overview: Bizzexpo is India’s largest B2B Marketplace offering instant B2B solutions through online business directory and yellow pages of Indian manufacturers, Indian suppliers & manufacturers, exporters. Find here quality products, trade leads, manufacturers, suppliers, exporters & international buyers.B2B refers to business to business marketing. Essentially, a B2B trade marketplace is a website that acts like a marketplace where importers, exporters, wholesalers, retailers, traders, distributors and any other business fraternity can get together for the purpose of conducting a business activity.
